//TEXT
<jaT0001>While I was puzzling over a plan to break this deadlock, I heard frantic footsteps. The worst report I had predicted was here.
<enT0001>While I was puzzling over a plan to break this deadlock, I heard frantic footsteps. The worst report I had predicted was here.

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0002>"Sempai! This is where you were!"
<enT0002>"Sempai! This is where you were!"

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0003>"Aah, Kazuhiko?"
<enT0003>"Aah, Kazuhiko?"

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0004>"Not 'Kazuhiko?'! I've been looking for you! They just entered all the key codes! The secondary control room is now under the control of the primary control room!"
<enT0004>"Not 'Kazuhiko?'! I've been looking for you! They just entered all the key codes! The secondary control room is now under the control of the primary control room!"

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0005>"I see..."
<enT0005>"I see..."

//TEXT
<jaT0006>Dumbfounded, I looked at my watch. We were well past the limit. I had tried to find a true solution until the very end. But now all we can do is sit and wait for our deaths.
<enT0006>Dumbfounded, I looked at my watch. We were well past the limit. I had tried to find a true solution until the very end. But now all we can do is sit and wait for our deaths.

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0007>"Not, 'I see'! Did you just idle our time away, and come up with nothing?!"
<enT0007>"Not, 'I see'! Did you just idle our time away, and come up with nothing?!"

//TEXT
<jaT0008>Kazuhiko glared at me with desperate eyes. I could only say but one word of reply, "Sorry".
<enT0008>Kazuhiko glared at me with desperate eyes. I could only say but one word of reply, "Sorry".

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0009>"However it seems we don't even have time to quarrel anymore. If they've taken control of the control room, then they've opened the fire doors?"
<enT0009>"However it seems we don't even have time to quarrel anymore. If they've taken control of the control room, then they've opened the fire doors?"

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0010>"Not 'Kazuhiko?'! The Sheratan's system won't take orders from the secondary control room. The primary control room has seized control."
<enT0010>"Not 'Kazuhiko?'! The Sheratan's system won't take orders from the secondary control room. The primary control room has seized control."

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0011>"I see..."
<enT0011>"I see..."

//TEXT
<jaT0012>Dumbfounded, I looked at my watch. We were well past the limit. I had tried to find a true solution until the very end. But now all we can do is sit and wait for our deaths.
<enT0012>Dumbfounded, I looked at my watch. We were well past the limit. I had tried to find a true solution until the very end. But now all we can do is sit and wait for our deaths.

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0013>"Why did this happen? Was this related to my job of observing the 3-D puzzle projected inside the computer?"
<enT0013>"Why did this happen? Was this related to my job of observing the 3-D puzzle projected inside the computer?"

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0014>"Well, it was. But it's too late now. If they've taken control of the control room, then they've opened the fire doors?"
<enT0014>"Well, it was. But it's too late now. If they've taken control of the control room, then they've opened the fire doors?"

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0015>"...Precisely."
<enT0015>"...Precisely."

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0016>"Return to the secondary control room. I'm heading directly to the fire door."
<enT0016>"Return to the secondary control room. I'm heading directly to the fire door."

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0017>"Eh? But..."
<enT0017>"Eh? But..."

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0018>"Just do it. Continue doing everything you can to take back control."
<enT0018>"Just do it. Continue doing everything you can to take back control."

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0019>"......"
<enT0019>"......"

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0020>"...Alright."
<enT0020>"...Alright."

//TEXT
<jaT0021>It seems he understood from my expression. Without saying anything more, Kazuhiko ran off.
<enT0021>It seems he understood from my expression. Without saying anything more, Kazuhiko ran off.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0022>"Now then. Time to give them one hell of a resistance."
<enT0022>"Now then. Time to give them one hell of a resistance."

//TEXT
<jaT0023>I wasn't completely without a plan. I thought about things in my own way...
<enT0023>I wasn't completely without a plan. I thought about things in my own way...

//TEXT
<jaT0024>I chose not to use that idea, so whether this is the end, or if I screw up and hasten Jararacas' invasion, either way, only despair lies ahead.
<enT0024>I chose not to use that idea, so whether this is the end, or if I screw up and hasten Jararacas' invasion, either way, only despair lies ahead.

//TEXT
<jaT0025>I wasn't completely without a plan. I thought about things in my own way...
<enT0025>I wasn't completely without a plan. I thought about things in my own way...

//TEXT
<jaT0026>I didn't have enough power, so whether this is the end, or if I screw up and hasten Jararacas' invasion, either way, only despair lies ahead.
<enT0026>I didn't have enough power, so whether this is the end, or if I screw up and hasten Jararacas' invasion, either way, only despair lies ahead.

//TEXT
<jaT0027>However, I have to take responsibility. Everyone followed my orders.
<enT0027>However, I have to take responsibility. Everyone followed my orders.

//TEXT
<jaT0028>Muttering those last words, I ran for my fight with no chance of victory.
<enT0028>Muttering those last words, I ran for my fight with no chance of victory.

